OL,3,CServing Guernsey police officer found
OL,4,Cguilty of assaulting teenager
OL,6,FA serving Guernsey police officer has
OL,7,Fbeen found guilty of assaulting a
OL,8,Fteenager outside St Sampson's High
OL,9,FSchool.
OL,11,FJesse Le Galloudec claimed he was
OL,12,Finnocent of the two counts of assault,
OL,13,Fbut the prosecution successfully
OL,14,Fproved that he pulled the 16-year-old
OL,15,Fboy off a moped before wrongfully
OL,16,Frestraining the teenager and taking
OL,17,Fhim to the floor.
