OL,3,CServing Guernsey police officer found
OL,4,Cguilty of assaulting teenager
OL,6,FLe Galloudec was off duty when the
OL,7,Fincident took place on 25 August 2024
OL,8,Fand he has continued to serve as a
OL,9,Fpolice officer since.
OL,11,FIt is agreed by both sides that the
OL,12,Fboy had mounted the pavement on a
OL,13,Fmoped, but the officer argued that the
OL,14,F16-year-old drove into him, so Le
OL,15,FGalloudec identified himself as police
OL,16,Fand then 'arrested' the teenager for
OL,17,Fdisorderly conduct.
