OL,3,CServing Guernsey police officer found
OL,4,Cguilty of assaulting teenager
OL,6,FThe incident began when Le Galloudec
OL,7,Fwas cleaning a family car at his home
OL,8,Flast summer and came out of his
OL,9,Fdriveway to see a teenager on a moped
OL,10,Fmount the pavement.
OL,12,FCCTV footage then shows the off-duty
OL,13,Fpolice officer standing in the road in
OL,14,Ffront of the moped, and holding his
OL,15,Farm out straight.
OL,17,FLe Galloudec argued that the 16-year-
OL,18,Fold drove into him, while the
OL,19,Fprosecution said he grabbed the boy.
