OL,3,CServing Guernsey police officer found
OL,4,Cguilty of assaulting teenager
OL,6,FThe driver lost control of the vehicle
OL,7,Fand skidded to a halt, damaging the
OL,8,Fmoped and injuring himself in the
OL,9,Fprocess.
OL,11,FA verbal altercation then followed,
OL,12,Fwhich was partially recorded on the
OL,13,Fteenager's mobile phone and widely
OL,14,Fshared on social media last year.
OL,16,FLe Galloudec announced he was a police
OL,17,Fofficer and arrested the teenager for
OL,18,Fdisorderly conduct.
